set system host-name policy-statement-to
set policy-options policy-statement PS term LEVEL to level 1
set policy-options policy-statement PS term LEVEL then accept
set policy-options policy-statement PS term LEVEL2 to level 2
set policy-options policy-statement PS term LEVEL2 then accept
set policy-options policy-statement PS term RIB to rib inet.0
set policy-options policy-statement PS term RIB then accept
set policy-options policy-statement PS term RIB6 to rib inet6.0
set policy-options policy-statement PS term RIB6 then accept
set policy-options policy-statement PS term PROTOCOL to protocol bgp
set policy-options policy-statement PS term PROTOCOL then accept
